## Actions
- Found `post_message` RPC in 20260419182000_infra_cleanup.sql had a
  phase-blackout that fired even for team-scoped writes.
- New migration 20260420160000_team_chat_blackout_bypass.sql:
  - `post_message`: when `p_team is not null`, skip the blackout entirely;
